Sally Rouse,*">Sally Rouse</a><sup>1,2*</sup></span><span class="author-wrapper notranslate"><img class=pr5 src='data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32"><rect fill-opacity="0"/></svg>' alt="Nichola C. Lacey" style="background-blend-mode:normal!important;background-clip:content-box!important;background-position:50% 50%!important;background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0)!important;background-image:var(--sf-img-7)!important;background-size:100% 100%!important;background-origin:content-box!important;background-repeat:no-repeat!important">Nichola C. Lacey<sup>1</sup></span><span class="author-wrapper notranslate"><img class=pr5 src='data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32"><rect fill-opacity="0"/></svg>' alt="Peter Hayes" style="background-blend-mode:normal!important;background-clip:content-box!important;background-position:50% 50%!important;background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0)!important;background-image:var(--sf-img-7)!important;background-size:100% 100%!important;background-origin:content-box!important;background-repeat:no-repeat!important">Peter Hayes<sup>2</sup></span><span class="author-wrapper notranslate"><a href=https://loop.frontiersin.org/people/705273 class=user-id-705273><img class=pr5 src="data:image/jpg;base64," alt="Thomas A. Wilding">Thomas A. Wilding</a><sup>1</sup></span></div>
